1
00:00:29,620 --> 00:00:32,980
=The Secret of the Lost Pearl=

2
00:00:33,020 --> 00:00:34,940
=Episode 23=
(Fiction. Do not imitate.)

3
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:40,060
(Xiangmu, Princess Xian'an)

4
00:00:41,670 --> 00:00:42,510
Chen!

5
00:00:47,110 --> 00:00:48,280
Chen, be careful!

6
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,790
Careful, Chen!

7
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:43,150
Come, come!

8
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,840
Come!

9
00:01:50,070 --> 00:01:50,910
Chen!

10
00:01:58,770 --> 00:01:59,680
Chen!

11
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:01,310
It's down!

12
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,710
Haven't you always wanted to know

13
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,310
what Chen Youxi's curse

14
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,840
has to do with this tomb?

15
00:02:17,000 --> 00:02:18,190
From the way you talk,

16
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,030
you already knew.

17
00:02:22,470 --> 00:02:23,840
Burial is to secure

18
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,310
and protect over time

19
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:28,563
and to keep the body intact
and the spirit safe,

20
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:31,400
so descendants flourish
and sacrifices never cease.

21
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,030
I don't understand.

22
00:02:33,306 --> 00:02:35,072
How do you understand
ancient Chinese texts?

23
00:02:35,310 --> 00:02:36,310
Not much,

24
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,000
just family teachings.

25
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:39,030
Family teachings?

26
00:02:39,870 --> 00:02:41,150
Are you trying to say

27
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:44,190
this tomb was built by your family?

28
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,400
My ancestors

29
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,240
have participated in building

30
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:52,190
imperial palaces

31
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,360
since the Qin dynasty.

32
00:02:53,910 --> 00:02:54,840
This tomb

33
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:57,080
was built for Princess Xian'an

34
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:58,910
by a predecessor named Bai Yao.

35
00:03:00,190 --> 00:03:02,000
Since you're a Bai descendant,

36
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,120
why destroy a tomb

37
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,470
built by your own ancestors?

38
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:08,120
In your eyes, it's destruction.

39
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,190
To me,

40
00:03:10,630 --> 00:03:11,960
it's inheriting their will.

41
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,590
What will?

42
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:20,150
Haven't you always wondered

43
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,080
why every trap in this tomb

44
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,400
can be solved?

45
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:25,470
Why?

46
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,120
Because the tomb builder

47
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:31,280
wanted to test and select

48
00:03:31,910 --> 00:03:33,000
someone capable

49
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,400
of fulfilling his will.

50
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,560
How so?

51
00:03:37,870 --> 00:03:39,836
The Bagua chambers Chen Youxi
and I went through

52
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:43,800
were to make us understand
our own value.

53
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:45,870
(Li)
Chen Youxi understood.

54
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,400
That's the first test.

55
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:50,430
The Bell Hall we passed through

56
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,080
can only be understood

57
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:54,310
and solved by the Bai descendants.

58
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,520
That's the second test.

59
00:03:57,030 --> 00:03:58,280
Getting the Lingxiao Pearl

60
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,910
and comprehending
the tomb's operating patterns

61
00:04:01,280 --> 00:04:02,566
(Zhen, Li)
to find the main hall

62
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,190
is the third test.

63
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,560
What exactly is the pattern
in the Bell Hall?

64
00:04:08,150 --> 00:04:10,400
It's our family's ancestral totem.

65
00:04:10,750 --> 00:04:12,870
Only if the tomb builder is sure

66
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,630
the visitor is a Bai descendant

67
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,750
will he trust them to fulfill the will

68
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,120
and move forward.

69
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:20,390
What is the will

70
00:04:20,666 --> 00:04:21,680
that you keep mentioning?

71
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:31,630
To resurrect Princess Xian'an.

72
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,870
That thing won't chase us again, right?

73
00:04:39,870 --> 00:04:41,000
I can't say for sure.

74
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,360
- This...
- Pah.

75
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:43,830
Can't you say something good?

76
00:04:44,373 --> 00:04:45,360
Shut your stinking mouth!

77
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,360
No, no!

78
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,600
The sound continues upward.

79
00:04:47,750 --> 00:04:49,310
The real main hall must be above.

80
00:04:49,550 --> 00:04:50,390
Let's go.

81
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,270
Come on.

82
00:04:51,750 --> 00:04:52,870
This is ridiculous.

83
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:54,720
You don't really believe

84
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,630
the dead can come back to life, do you?

85
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:03,270
A giant spider with combat awareness,

86
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,310
a tomb operating for a thousand years,

87
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,920
and Chen Youxi's curse...

88
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,000
If you hadn't seen it yourself,

89
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:15,310
wouldn't it all seem like a legend?

90
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,830
You followed Chen Youxi,

91
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:21,720
leaving Professor Chen,

92
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,430
and putting aside scientific treatments,

93
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:27,160
because you believed

94
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,270
some unknown power

95
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:32,560
could lift his curse, right?

96
00:05:33,950 --> 00:05:35,190
Professor Chen?

97
00:05:36,496 --> 00:05:38,000
A few days before I returned to China,

98
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:40,040
his condition suddenly improved.

99
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:41,830
Could it have been you?

100
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,040
Yes.

101
00:05:43,196 --> 00:05:44,720
I arranged for him to get the medicine

102
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,600
that could temporarily control
his condition.

103
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,230
So,

104
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,920
you also made Chen Youxi

105
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,070
suddenly fall ill?

106
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,390
I gave him the embroidered shoes.

107
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,270
You claim to be a Bai descendant,

108
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,430
but from observing you,

109
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:00,800
I think you don't know much

110
00:06:00,811 --> 00:06:03,084
about the tomb's structure, location,
or even the traps.

111
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,950
This shows

112
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,270
your inherited will and maps

113
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:09,240
are partially incomplete.

114
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,040
After a thousand years,

115
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,000
that's reasonable.

116
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,950
So, you wanted to use Chen Youxi

117
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,240
to locate the tomb

118
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:17,510
and solve the traps.

119
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,270
That's fine.

120
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:22,040
But I don't understand one thing:

121
00:06:22,950 --> 00:06:23,800
Why use

122
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,390
Chen Youxi's worsening illness

123
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,000
to bring me back to China?

124
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,430
Because

125
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,830
I need your blood.

126
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,520
Blood?

127
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,070
According to Bai Yao's records,

128
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:41,720
resurrecting the princess

129
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,390
requires three conditions:

130
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,360
the blood moon night,
the Lingxiao Pearl,

131
00:06:46,630 --> 00:06:48,310
and the blood of a Caligonga.

132
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:50,430
A Caligonga...

133
00:06:50,713 --> 00:06:51,859
You've got the wrong person.

134
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:53,800
I was born abroad,

135
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:55,630
not a Caligonga.

136
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,680
Before entering the Nether Ruins,

137
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:58,920
I'd never been to China.

138
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:01,680
Your grandfather is Mr. Zhe, right?

139
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:04,390
He was born a Caligonga

140
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,870
and later emigrated abroad.

141
00:07:06,166 --> 00:07:08,012
Thousands of years ago
in the Western regions,

142
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,630
Caligonga live sacrifices were used

143
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,390
for resurrection rituals.

144
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:15,230
I see.

145
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:19,310
She plans to use Ms. He
as the sacrifice.

146
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,110
I'll fight them!

147
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,560
Why?

148
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:24,240
Don't you see?

149
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:27,360
He has a machine gun.

150
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,390
How do you fight him bare-handed?

151
00:07:30,270 --> 00:07:31,600
That was thousands of years ago.

152
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,310
People didn't understand science,

153
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,430
so they resorted
to killing and sacrifices,

154
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,360
using faith in gods to establish belief.

155
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:41,070
If the princess
could really be resurrected,

156
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:43,560
why didn't your ancestor do it?

157
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:45,920
Why wait a thousand years for you?

158
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:47,950
Because in his lifetime,

159
00:07:48,612 --> 00:07:50,199
he couldn't gather the three conditions.

160
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,480
He devoted his life

161
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,430
to building this extraordinary tomb,

162
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:56,750
waiting for this day,

163
00:07:57,630 --> 00:07:58,750
waiting for his descendants

164
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,680
to gather the three conditions

165
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,680
and fulfill this great wish.

166
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:04,760
You're insane.

167
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:11,870
Shutong, like you,

168
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,310
I lived abroad since childhood,

169
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:17,190
knowing little of my ancestors.

170
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,310
I struggled to get here.

171
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:24,510
Am I not entitled to know the truth?

172
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:28,120
She's insane.

173
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,360
Let's send her to a mental hospital.

174
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:35,960
What are you doing?

175
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,360
Bai Lingling, listen.

176
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:43,200
Don't move.

177
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,280
Don't move!

178
00:08:49,910 --> 00:08:50,910
Wait!

179
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:53,110
Who?

180
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,040
It's me!

181
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,150
I'm Lu Di.

182
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,910
I'm telling you.

183
00:08:58,240 --> 00:09:00,720
The Lingxiao Pearl
in your hands is fake.

184
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:06,710
Come out.

185
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:08,360
Don't shoot.

186
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:09,550
I'm coming out.

187
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,470
Don't shoot!

188
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,120
Don't shoot.

189
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,510
Let's talk.

190
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,350
Come out.

191
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:16,390
I'm coming out.

192
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:18,390
Bro.

193
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,200
Bro, don't be rash!

194
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,510
They sent you again.

195
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,160
What about those two?

196
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:37,960
Those two?

197
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:42,240
The giant spider ate them.

198
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:43,350
What?

199
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,600
On our way back,

200
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:46,790
we ran into the spider.

201
00:09:46,790 --> 00:09:48,440
They're both dead.

202
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:49,870
What did you just say?

203
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,906
They were eaten by the spider.

204
00:09:52,917 --> 00:09:53,983
I'm asking about the pearl.

205
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:55,270
Oh.

206
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,790
Yes, the pearl.

207
00:09:57,150 --> 00:09:57,990
Miss Bai,

208
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,790
sorry about this.

209
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:02,630
I'm utterly ruthless for money.

210
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:05,080
I secretly swapped your pearl.

211
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,030
The one in your hand is fake.

212
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,120
Nonsense!

213
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,670
Look, at this point,

214
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:11,200
how could I lie to you?

215
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:13,270
I can't get out alone.

216
00:10:13,270 --> 00:10:15,360
With this body, I'd die here.

217
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,440
I figured

218
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,510
you have numbers

219
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:19,270
and a machine gun,

220
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:20,600
so I should stick with you

221
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,840
to get out.

222
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,790
Enough talk.

223
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:24,320
Where's the pearl?

224
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:25,910
Where's the pearl?

225
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:27,790
My pearl...

226
00:10:27,950 --> 00:10:28,790
Take it out!

227
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:29,750
Here.

228
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,280
Come on.

229
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,200
Open it.

230
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,790
I'm letting you open it!

231
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:39,670
Sure.

232
00:10:39,670 --> 00:10:40,510
Wait.

233
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,120
Why...

234
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,510
Hurry up!

235
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:51,480
I'm opening it.

236
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:02,750
Weren't they eaten by the spider?

237
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:05,560
Fine.

238
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,750
If you don't come out,

239
00:11:08,510 --> 00:11:10,150
I'll shoot him!

240
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:20,860
Crap!

241
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,230
Chen Youxi!

242
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,840
Watch out!

243
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,080
Don't move!

244
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,360
I have the Lingxiao Pearl now.

245
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:04,630
Release them,

246
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,360
or I'll throw it.

247
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,360
If you dare throw it,

248
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,600
I'll kill her first.

249
00:12:08,720 --> 00:12:09,560
You wouldn't.

250
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,550
If you want the princess resurrected,

251
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:13,240
you have to get this pearl.

252
00:12:14,550 --> 00:12:15,600
Miss Bai!

253
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,840
Miss Bai,

254
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:19,320
we heard everything you said just now.

255
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,030
This is nonsense.

256
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,480
It's a feudal superstition
causing death.

257
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:24,960
Chen Youxi,

258
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,670
since you heard that,

259
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:27,960
you should understand

260
00:12:28,026 --> 00:12:29,329
what the princess's resurrection

261
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,440
means to you.

262
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,150
For you,

263
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:37,790
living is most important.

264
00:12:40,030 --> 00:12:41,120
For me, it's not.

265
00:12:44,630 --> 00:12:45,670
You can have the pearl.

266
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,030
First, release them.

267
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,429
Give me the Lingxiao Pearl first,

268
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,280
or...

269
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,670
If you hurt them, I...

270
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:52,600
What can you do?

271
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:53,590
Huang Long!

272
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:56,670
Who goes first?

273
00:13:01,030 --> 00:13:03,030
No, he...

274
00:13:03,870 --> 00:13:05,600
Chen,

275
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,910
she only needs a drop of Ms. He's blood.

276
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:08,870
Just pierce her finger

277
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,750
and squeeze a few drops.

278
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:11,670
Shut up.

279
00:13:12,069 --> 00:13:13,349
What if she wants a whole basin?

280
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,750
Why not add some water?

281
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:15,630
Shut up.

282
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,000
Do it.

283
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:19,840
Bai Lingling!

284
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:27,670
I don't want to hurt

285
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:28,790
any of you.

286
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,200
We can all get what we need.

287
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:31,550
Give me the pearl first.

288
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,240
Okay. You can have the pearl.

289
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,840
Watch out!

290
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:40,120
Lu, are you okay?

291
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:53,630
Stop.

292
00:15:57,739 --> 00:15:59,869
The chance to witness
the Lingxiao Pearl's true power

293
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:00,840
is right in front of us!

294
00:16:05,630 --> 00:16:06,470
Shutong,

